{
  "id": "adv_card_ktn_08_02",
  "title": "長瀬琴乃 2話 大事にしないで下さい",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日　月ストのレッスン後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The next day‚ after Moon Tempest’s lesson",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "……という感じで、練習は順調でした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…In this way‚ the practice was going well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.1999999444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "分かった、報告ありがとう\nそれじゃあ、お疲れ……ん？　どうしたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Got it‚ thanks for the report.\nSo‚ good work… Hm? What’s wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.2333335003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "えっと、ちょっとお話が……\nあ、いえ、別に大した話じゃないんですけど……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ I have something to tell…\nOh‚ well‚ it’s not that important…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.4000007392,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "……こほん。{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Uhm. {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.8000016292,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "お……おと……お……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-New… N-New… N…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.5333376329,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "お……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "New…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.2333378872,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "お正月と聞いて、何を思い浮かべますか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What comes to mind when you think of New Year’s!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.4333378872,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ど、どうしたんだ急に？　お正月というと……\nサニピのカウントダウンライブは今でも覚えているが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-what’s with the sudden question? New Year’s…\nI still remember Sunny Peace’s countdown live.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.2666712206,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、あのライブは良かったですよね\nみんなとってもキラキラしてて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ that live show was good!\nEveryone was so sparkly…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.8666742724,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "曲中にカウントダウンのコールを入れるのは\nサニピに凄くよく合ってますよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Putting a countdown call in the middle of the song\nreally suited Sunny Peace.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.0666735095,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "あんな風にファンを楽しく巻き込むことが\n出来るのはサニピの強みで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Being able to get the fans involved\nlike that is Sunny Peace’s strength…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.7333429736,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "……って、そうじゃないです！\nもう、何を言ってるんですか！　全然違いますよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That’s not what I meant!\nWhat are you talking about! It’s completely different!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.5333439908,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "全然違うのか！？　す、すまない\n……いや、なんで俺は今怒られたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Completely different!? S-sorry…\n…Wait‚ why am I getting scolded?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.4666869881,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9833.324178000012,
          "startTime": 84.3000111661
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "も、もういいです、出直してきます！\nちゃんと言えなかった私も悪いですし！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-never mind‚ I’ll come back later!\nIt’s my fault for not being able to say it properly!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.4666880054,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7266.645327899994,
          "startTime": 88.7333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃のやつ、どうしたんだ……？\n……って、あれ、すず。何か用事か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s gotten into Kotono…?\n…Oh‚ Suzu. What’s up?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.2333389046,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "お年玉がほしい……ってこの間あげただろ\n二回目があってもいいじゃないかって……あのなぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You want New Year’s money…? But I already gave you some.\nYou want more? …Come on…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.7333368701,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5346.669869099997,
          "startTime": 104.0800067392
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "ずるい！　二回目なんて……！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s not fair! More…!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.2333389045,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "こ、琴乃……？　さっきから様子が変だぞ……？\n何か悩みがあるなら、聞かせてほしいんだが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "K-Kotono…? You’ve been acting strange…\nIf you have something on your mind‚ you can tell me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.3333389045,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9333.328906600002,
          "startTime": 120.6666678111
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ……なんでもないです、私は大丈夫ですから！\nよいお年を！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "U-um… It’s nothing‚ I’m fine!\nSee you next year!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.4333343269,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "今年は始まったばかりだぞ！？　って、行ってしまった\n一体どうしたんだ琴乃は……ちょっと心配だな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s only the beginning of the new year!? …She left.\nWhat’s wrong with Kotono… I’m a little worried.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.1333343269,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――後日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.9333383959,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1066.652425100017,
          "startTime": 133.999990821
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1466.6616041000111,
          "startTime": 134.4
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.9333241543
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.9333241543
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "失礼します。私に話があると聞いたんですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Excuse me. I heard you wanted to talk to me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.9999959072,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.4333292406
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "あ、今度のグラビア撮影の話でしょうか？\n確かにそろそろ打ち合わせしないといけませんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ is this about the next gravure photo shoot?\nWe should definitely have a meeting about it soon.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.2999959072,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02-ktn015.m4a",
      "text": "星見市の頃に着た着物風の衣装を\nもう一度着るんですよね。とっても楽しみにして――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're wearing the kimono-style outfits we wore in Hoshimi city before‚ right?\nI've been really looking forward to it――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.5333211025,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 154.5999796312
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "その話は後回しだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ll talk about that later.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.5999796312,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02-ktn016.m4a",
      "text": "え？　えっと、どういうことですか？\nまた別の用件が……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Um‚ what do you mean?\nIs there something else…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.9000060798,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 165.0333160163
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "単刀直入に聞こう\n琴乃……やはり何か悩みがあるんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll get straight to the point.\nKotono… Is there something bothering you?",
